## Status Codes Monitored

| Code | Meaning | Why It Matters |
|---|---|---|
| 401 | Unauthorized | Failed login attempts |
| 403 | Forbidden | Accessing restricted resources |
| 404 | Not Found | Probing for hidden pages |
| 500 | Server Error | Possible malicious input |

